CustomField.description: The number of seconds of hunt time incurred by calls received by the organisation from the outside world, regardless of whether they have been connected or not to a User. No Natterbox User will ever be associated with this call statistic, as purely measures inbound traffic.
CustomField.inlineHelpText: How many seconds have callers calling into my organisation been spending waiting to talk to a real person
CustomField.label: Inbound Hunt Seconds
